---
title: Smoky Beef Cheeseburgers with Potato Wedges and Caramelized Onions
description: This classic diner meal becomes next-level delicious with the addition of smoky flavours courtesy of smoked paprika-garlic dusted potato wedges and a creamy BBQ mayo! Topped with caramelized onions, these burgers are sure to earn a place among your family’s favourites
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-au-fromage-et-au-boeuf-fume-2ae7c8d0.jpg
